/**
 * completeDeleteAccount — AUTHORITATIVE account deletion endpoint.
 *
 * Deletes ALL user-owned data across every entity, resets the User profile
 * to a clean "deleted" state, and writes a tombstone for audit.
 *
 * CRITICAL FOR GMAIL REUSE:
 *   - Sets account_status = 'deleted' and onboarding_complete = false
 *   - Clears all PII fields on the User record
 *   - Tombstone stores only hashed email (no PII)
 *   - When same Gmail signs in again via OAuth, AuthCallback detects tombstone,
 *     calls clearDeletedUserTombstone which resets account_status to 'active'
 *     and sends user to fresh onboarding
 *
