 * computeRecipePricingV2 — Production-Grade Unified Pricing Engine
 * 
 * PART 3-6: CANONICAL MATCHING + QUANTITY NORMALIZATION + PRICE RESOLUTION + CALCULATION
 * 
 * Replaces fragmented pricing logic with a deterministic, observable, scalable pipeline.
 * 
 * Input: recipe (with ingredients list)
 * Output: 
 *   - RecipePricingSummary (total_cost, cost_per_serving, coverage)
 *   - RecipeIngredientPricing records (per-ingredient audit trail)
 *   - observability (unresolved, anomalies, fallback rate)
 * 
 * Scaling strategy:
 * - idempotent (same inputs = same outputs)
 * - cacheable (canonical match cache, price source cache)
 * - batchable (multiple recipes via background job)
 * - versioned (pricing_version field allows engine upgrades without drift)
 */

