 * ARCHITECTURE:
 *   Every cost-producing code path calls this BEFORE executing the expensive operation.
 *   Returns { allowed: true/false, mode, scope_key, reason }.
 *
 * MODES (stored in AppConfig entity, key = "cost_enforcement"):
